<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10498795>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Synagris rufopicta Tullgren, female paralectotype of S. parvula von Schulthess. a, habitus in dorsal view. b, habitus in lateral view. c, head in frontal view. d, labels. Credits: Harald Schillhammer and Manuela Vizek, NHMW, 2023." ;
